## §6. ATTACK SURFACE / SECURITY

### §6.1 XSS risk
- Sử dụng `innerHTML` trong `logTerm()` với template literal → OK vì msg controlled
- Template literal `${screen.name}` trong card HTML → **POTENTIAL XSS** nếu screenData từ API untrusted
  - Line 507: `card-${screen.id}`, `title="${screen.name}"`, `${screen.name}`
  - Mitigation: escape HTML hoặc dùng textContent

### §6.2 LocalStorage safety
- Only stores audit state (checkbox values) → low risk
- Không lưu credentials, tokens → OK

### §6.3 External dependencies
- Tailwind CDN: `https://cdn.tailwindcss.com` (official)
- Google Fonts: Inter + JetBrains Mono (official)
- Không có untrusted 3rd party scripts → OK

**Overall security:** OK cho internal dev tool, cần XSS fix nếu deploy production.

